   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;h5&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46885308_1" alt="" width="358" height="134" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Instructions to Students&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;Answer all &lt;/span&gt;the questions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Put your responses in the spaces provided.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Your responses must be &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;in your own words&lt;/span&gt;, and should be a &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;maximum of fifty words&lt;/span&gt; in length, or a sentence or two on each part of your answer. &lt;br&gt;Q22 may require a longer answer. Use appropritate cyber terms and avoid one or two word answers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Referencing is not applicable, and any &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;cut and paste responses are invalid&lt;/span&gt; (all your answers must be in your own words&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;For multipart answers, use bullet points to format your answer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
